Here is the translation:

He settles in his own place, pleases his people's mind; 
He has made his village beautiful, he came as a lovely youth.

Here is the translation:

After adornment with virtues, make your soul beautiful; 
After being entangled in worldly affairs, one gets stuck in their own heart, without leaving a remnant.

Tiyaan baporriya anjavale, nath sabha upha thai baale;
Aaj maal ya manush apara, bahu purush ne bahunary.

It is evening at Tiyaan, the darkness will spread; 
Today a great human has come, many men have got many wives.
